<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/297936-is-this-a-revised-edition-of-the-2008-or">Is this a revised edition of the 2008 or 2009 books with the same name? Or, is this version for an American (as opposed to British) audience?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_297936'><a id="like_count_community_question_297936" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/297936?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F3272165-bad-science">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/297936-is-this-a-revised-edition-of-the-2008-or">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
