  <span id="freeText8573394943053650137" style="display:none">A fun, easy, and informative read that works to explain why nonsense is so popular and widespread and how 'bad science' can have a massive cultural impact and, unfortunately, cause a lot of unnecessary pain and suffering. Too bad the people who most need to read this book would likely never pick it up.</span>
